--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1)UPDATE THE PRICE OF A PARTICULAR PRODUCT

mysql> SELECT * FROM PRODUCT;
+-----+------------+-------+
| PID | PNAME      | PRICE |
+-----+------------+-------+
|   1 | HORLICKS   |   204 |
|   2 | BOOST      |   122 |
|   3 | COMPLAN    |   122 |
|   4 | BONVITA    |   235 |
|   5 | CORNFLAKES |    82 |
+-----+------------+-------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> UPDATE PRODUCT SET PRICE=100 WHERE PNAME='BOOST';
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.08 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

mysql> SELECT * FROM PRODUCT;
+-----+------------+-------+
| PID | PNAME      | PRICE |
+-----+------------+-------+
|   1 | HORLICKS   |   204 |
|   2 | BOOST      |   100 |
|   3 | COMPLAN    |   122 |
|   4 | BONVITA    |   235 |
|   5 | CORNFLAKES |    82 |
+-----+------------+-------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 2)CHANGE THE NAME OF CITY  'CLT' TO KOZHIKODE IN THE CUSTOMER TABLE

mysql> SELECT * FROM  CUSTOMER;
+----+-------+-------------+----------+---------+
| ID | NAME  | ADDRESS     | CITY     | PH_NO   |
+----+-------+-------------+----------+---------+
|  1 | ANAND | OAM NIVAS10 | VATAKARA |  828196 |
|  2 | ASWIN | VKP110      | EKM      |  910106 |
|  3 | ABIN  | HHHT14      | TVM      |   12367 |
|  4 | MANU  | KL12        | CLT      | 8123467 |
|  5 | ARJUN | KL14        | VALAT    |  566787 |
|  6 | SHIBU | KL17        | IDY      | 4567887 |
|  7 | SUBUU | KL37        | WLUYY    |    NULL |
+----+-------+-------------+----------+---------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> UPDATE CUSTOMER SET CITY='KOZHIKODE' WHERE ID=4; //WRONG
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.04 sec)
Rows matched: 1  Changed: 1  Warnings: 0

mysql> SELECT * FROM CUSTOMER;
+----+-------+-------------+-----------+---------+
| ID | NAME  | ADDRESS     | CITY      | PH_NO   |
+----+-------+-------------+-----------+---------+
|  1 | ANAND | OAM NIVAS10 | VATAKARA  |  828196 |
|  2 | ASWIN | VKP110      | EKM       |  910106 |
|  3 | ABIN  | HHHT14      | TVM       |   12367 |
|  4 | MANU  | KL12        | KOZHIKODE | 8123467 |
|  5 | ARJUN | KL14        | VALAT     |  566787 |
|  6 | SHIBU | KL17        | IDY       | 4567887 |
|  7 | SUBUU | KL37        | WLUYY     |    NULL |
+----+-------+-------------+-----------+---------+
7 rows in set (0.00 sec)

